WEBVTT

00:00.037 --> 00:01.834
<i>Previously on Bates Motel...</i>

00:01.859 --> 00:02.969
Norman!

00:03.231 --> 00:04.441
What happened last night?

00:04.453 --> 00:07.397
You said something about Ms. Watson
was going to give you a ride home.

00:07.422 --> 00:10.129
I don't remember. I just
remember running home.

00:10.166 --> 00:11.800
- Why?
- Ms. Watson is dead.

00:12.259 --> 00:13.869
I am looking for Norma Bates.

00:13.993 --> 00:15.528
- Who are you?
- I'm her brother.

00:19.033 --> 00:20.330
Get out!

00:20.367 --> 00:21.802
- He's your brother.
- He raped me.

00:21.834 --> 00:23.905
- You're unbelievable.
- He raped me, Dylan!

00:23.918 --> 00:25.140
I don't believe you!

00:26.076 --> 00:27.298
Get away from her!

00:28.109 --> 00:29.294
She's lying. Can't you see that?

00:29.319 --> 00:30.741
Norman, stop it!

00:30.753 --> 00:33.024
He can't help it! It's his dad!

00:33.031 --> 00:34.628
Caleb is his dad.

00:36.736 --> 00:38.345
Why are you doing this to me, huh?

00:39.156 --> 00:41.763
- Get in.
- You got the wrong person!

00:42.434 --> 00:44.206
Norman!

00:44.243 --> 00:46.526
You really shouldn't tell
anyone that you came here.

00:46.551 --> 00:47.998
You know what you have to do.

00:48.484 --> 00:49.981
I'm always with you.

00:50.418 --> 00:52.127
There's something wrong with me. I'm bad.

00:52.139 --> 00:54.023
You never meant to hurt
anybody in you life.

00:54.050 --> 00:55.697
- But I did.
- You have these blackouts

00:55.722 --> 00:57.019
and they confuse you.

00:57.056 --> 00:59.102
Do a polygraph on this kid. For me.

00:59.127 --> 01:01.011
- Is your name Norman Bates?
- Yes.

01:01.035 --> 01:02.495
Did you kill Blaire Watson?

01:02.520 --> 01:03.655
Norman...

01:03.800 --> 01:06.057
Norman. Norman.

01:06.793 --> 01:08.452
You need to know something very important.

01:08.515 --> 01:10.074
You didn't kill Blaire Watson.

01:10.124 --> 01:11.795
- I did.
- You did?

01:11.833 --> 01:13.879
We have to keep this a secret.

01:13.923 --> 01:15.420
Do you promise?

01:15.795 --> 01:17.379
I promise.

